These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: dog, snake, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, surfing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the owner of the snake##2
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Pet      | snake | goldfish | dog |
| Sport   | surfing     | handball    | lacrosse   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, apricot
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, dahlia, tulip
1. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who likes ivory##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Color   | ivory    | apricot        | brown |
| Flower     | dahlia | tulip | daisy         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: yellow, brown, red
House: modern, futuristic, wooden
1. the modern house is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person who likes yellow is between the futuristic house and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Color   | brown | yellow     | red |
| House        | futuristic  | wooden | modern |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
City: berlin, liverpool, nizza
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, aconite, daffodil
1. the person traveling to berlin is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is between the person who growsaconite and the person who growsbegonia##2
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| City   | liverpool  | nizza     | berlin |
| Flower           | aconite | daffodil | begonia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, coach, designer
City: london, venice, miami
1. the designer is on the left of the scientist##1
2. the designer is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to miami and the person traveling to venice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Job   | coach | designer     | scientist |
| City     | miami    | london | venice    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, subway, snowmobile
1. the person driving the taxi is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the lizard##2
2. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the subway##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Pet   | lizard  | snake   | hedgehog        |
| Transport         | subway | taxi | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, poker
3 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person playing poker and the owner of the hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Game          | canasta  | bridge  | poker |
| Pet   | hedgehog | cat | horse     |

