.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, lawyer, social-worker
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking milk##2
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite  | almond-milk  |
| Job   | pilot | lawyer | social-worker |

