.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, collecting, traveling
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, august
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Hobby       | traveling | video-games | collecting  |
| Birthday   | august    | september        | may |

