There are 3 different favourite colors: green, red, coral
1. the person who likes coral is between the chinese and the person who likes green##2
2. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | chinese | thai      | american      |
| Color       | red  | coral | green |

