.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, volleyball, handball
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, western, superhero
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person watching superhero movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Sport   | volleyball  | parkour   | handball  |
| Movie-Genre        | western | mystery | superhero |

