.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, backgammon
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, davidoff, baccarat
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing backgammon and the davidoff-smoker##2
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Game      | backgammon | scrabble   | snooker |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | bluemaster | davidoff   |

 